\f0\fs56 \cf0 We annotate multiword expressions (MWEs) in Prague Dependency Treebank ( \f1 \uc0\u10122 \f0 ).\ We use PML scheme to capture the annotation of whole PDT as well as of our MWEs ( \f1 \uc0\u10123 \f0 ).\ Our annotators work with an annotation tool ( \f1 \uc0\u10126 \f0 ) and mark occurences in sentences, which are generated from the deep syntactic layer (t-layer) of PDT: see \f1 \uc0\u10122 \f0 , \f1 \uc0\u10123 \f0 , \f1 \uc0\u10125 \f0 .\ Our aim is to improve a representation of MWEs (incl. named entities) in t-trees ( \f1 \uc0\u10124 \f0 ), because current approach is considered to be insufficient ( \f1 \uc0\u10127 \f0 ).\ \ \ }
